title: Inglis Dishwasher INLET VALVE
description: Inglis Dishwasher INLET VALVE ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 30 Reviews PartSelect Number PS12578165 Manufacturer Part Number W11175771 This water inlet valve should be located behind the lower kick plate panel in either the right or left corner. The attaching solenoids on the valve open and close according to the desired amount of water needed.

installationInstructions.author: Melissa from AIKEN, SC
installationInstructions.title: Inlet valve wasn't working
installationInstructions.content: Put thread tape on threads. Screwed water hose to part. Pushed hose onto part. Pushed electric clip to part. Screwed part onto washer. Done
